## ğŸ“‚ Folder Structure

```
/your_flask_project
â”‚â”€â”€ app.py                # Main Flask app file
â”‚â”€â”€ templates/
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ index.html        # Main template file
â”‚â”€â”€ static/               # CSS, JS, images, etc.
â”‚â”€â”€ edits.json            # EditableFlask Edits saved (EditableFlask Managed)
â”‚â”€â”€ intents/              # SQLite database (if used)
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ *.db              # Database File (EditableFlask Managed)
```

For more details, refer to the [Flask Documentation](https://flask.palletsprojects.com/).

